          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-D"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The quasimonoenergetic neutron beam was produced",
                " via the 2H(d,n)3He reaction by bombarding a deuterium",
                " gas target with a deuteron beam at currents aprx 1-2",
                " mu-A. Neutron flux varied between 3.E+05 and",
                " 4.E+06 n/(cm2 s) in the four runs performed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "79-AU-197",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.9999
              },
              "free_text": [
                " High-purity natural gold foils",
                " <99.99% 197Au> with a diameter of 14 mm and thickness",
                " of 0.5 mm were used. Two Al foils of the same",
                " diameter and thickness were placed immediately before",
                " and after the gold foil and were used to determine",
                " the neutron flux."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Four irradiations have been carried out.",
                " The SULSA unfolding code was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG,,,EVAL",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG,,,EVAL",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24",
                        "target": "13-AL-27",
                        "projectile": "N",
                        "process": "A",
                        "product": "11-NA-24",
                        "quantity": ",SIG",
                        "data_type": "EVAL",
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",SIG"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The integrated neutron flux was determined by using",
                " the cross-section values for the 27Al(n,alpha)24Na",
                " reaction found in literature (see MONIT-REF) and by",
                " averaging over the deduced values in the front",
                " and back Al foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
