              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The induced activity on the samples was measured",
                " with a 56% relative efficiency high-purity germanium",
                " (HPGe) detector. The detector was calibrated with",
                " 152Eu and 207Bi sources."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Beam fluctuations were monitored with a BF3",
